Modifications.Value: Alas, after a hard-fought battle that slaughtered many humans and gave the walls of the Niffy a free coating of red blood (it was quite flattering, I must assure you) the alien was finally vanquished. The humans did rejoice!|nBut wait! Look, the alien transformed into a plane...thing!|nAnd the humans did chuckle merrily, and could not bring themselves to kill the alien because of their laughter. Unfortunately, two minutes later the alien regenerated into a hulking mass of evil again. And together the aliens and the humans finished the Niffy's new paint-job!
